<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Eventos - Conecta Eventos</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #2C3E50;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #2C3E50;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .logo img {
      height: 30px;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      margin: 0 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    nav a:hover,
    nav a.active {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .btn-sair {
      background-color: white;
      color: #2C3E50;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    main {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .highlight {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      background-color: white;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .highlight-text {
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    .highlight-text h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .highlight-text p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .highlight-img img {
      max-width: 300px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
    }

    .highlight button {
      background-color: #2C3E50;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .event-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      background-color: #2C3E50;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .event-card:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: #e74c3c;
      flex-direction: row-reverse;
    }

    .event-info {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .event-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .event-date {
      font-size: 1rem;
      background-color: transparent;
      border: 2px solid #f1c40f;
      color: #f1c40f;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .event-card:nth-child(even) .event-date {
      border-color: #fff;
      color: white;
    }

    .event-card button {
      background-color: white;
      color: #2C3E50;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .event-img img {
      max-width: 160px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #888;
      padding: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .highlight {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .event-card {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .event-card:nth-child(even) {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .event-img img {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="logobranca.svg" alt="Logo Conecta Eventos" />
      <strong>CONECTA EVENTOS</strong>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/eventos" class="active">Eventos</a>
      <a href="/criar">Criar Eventos</a>
      <a href="/inscritos">Eventos Inscritos</a>
    </nav>
    <button class="btn-sair" onclick="window.location.href='/login'">Sair</button>
  </header>

  <main>

    <section class="highlight">
      <div class="highlight-text">
        <h2>Descubra Eventos Incríveis. <br> Participe. Conecte-se.</h2>
        <p>Encontre os melhores eventos, palestras e workshops em um só lugar. Cadastre-se agora e garanta sua vaga nas experiências que vão transformar sua jornada.</p>
        <button onclick="alert('Inscrição iniciada')">Inscrever</button>
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-img">
        <img src="../public/evento_principal.ejs.svg" alt="Evento principal">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="event-card">
      <div class="event-img">
        <img src="evento_bussines.svg" alt="Business Talks">
      </div>
      <div class="event-info">
        <div class="event-title">BUSINESS <span style="color: #f1c40f;">TALKS</span></div>
        <div class="event-date">Seg | 10:00 AM | 12 de Junho</div>
        <button>Inscrever - se</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="event-card">
      <div class="event-img">
        <img src="imagen_webnar.svg" alt="Webinar Conference">
      </div>
      <div class="event-info">
        <div class="event-title">WEBINAR <span style="color: #ffd5d5;">CONFERENCE</span></div>
        <div class="event-date">Seg | 07:00 AM | Mon de Janeiro</div>
        <button>Inscrever - se</button>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <footer>
    Copyright © 2025 | Conecta Eventos
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
